metadata.name: Nft in America Super VIP ticket | 01/20
metadata.description: This is the 01/20 Super VIP ticket of the event ‘Nft in America 2022’. Artwork by Jonathan Plesel. For more info & see the benefits of this ticket: https://nft-in.com | If you own this ticket, please contact supervip@nft-in.com to get all the associated benefits. ’NFT in America 2022’: March 25, 2022 at Montalban Theater, Hollywood. In case of a postponed event, tickets will be transferred to the new event date.
